data.description: WELCOME TO THIS ADORABLE 3 BEDROOM 2 BATHROOM MOVE-IN-READY HOME IN DESIRABLE LEVITT PARK! NO HOA! As soon as you walk in, you can envision your family living here! This home features a great open floor plan w/ Pergo wood flooring & tile w/ terrazzo flooring under!  Spacious kitchen w/ laundry room directly off of it leading to the garage! Each bedroom is light & bright & is perfect for a growing family! Enjoy the Florida weather & lifestyle in your screened-in porch overlooking a fully fenced-in backyard! Large enough for a pool! Solar panels save on electricity & add to the functionality of this beautiful home! Roof - 2015, AC - 2022, HWH - 2016, Solar Panels - 2022. MAKE YOUR APPOINTMENT NOW & MAKE THIS HOME YOURS!
